                <div class="projectContentDescription">
                    <p><strong>Web API Demo Application:</strong></p>
                    <p>
                        "Web API Demo Application" is one part of a two part program that demonstrates the use of a basic CRUD API call.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Part 1 contains a .NET application that runs a Web API, which connects to a local database.
                        Part 2 contains a .NET Winform application that makes a call to our separate Web API, takes the information received, then renders it into a DataView Grid table.
